# Cloudaffle Blog Homepage

A responsive blog homepage built using pure HTML and CSS.  
This is my first frontend webpage project where I practiced layout design, Flexbox, responsive design, reusable components, and semantic HTML structure.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Responsive blog homepage layout
- Hero section with featured article
- Blog cards section
- Navigation bar with search box
- Footer section
- Hover effects and transitions
- Mobile and tablet responsive design
- Clean UI using Flexbox

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Flexbox
- Media Queries
- Google Fonts
- Material Symbols Icons

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```bash
project-folder/
│
├── index.html
├── images/
├── styles/
│   ├── css-reset.css
│   ├── variables.css
│   ├── style.css
│   ├── mobile.css
│   └── tablet.css
```

---

## 📱 Responsive Design

This project includes:

- Desktop layout
- Tablet layout
- Mobile layout

Using media queries for better user experience across devices.

---

